# Maintaining docs/theory/

> High-level principles: `dev-notes/design/agent_instructions_design.md`

`docs/theory/` contains **mathematical derivations** in MyST Markdown (`.md`),
based on [Shi2016]. These are the formal mathematical foundations for the
distributions and algorithms implemented in normix.

