| `gig.md` | Generalized Inverse Gaussian | `tutorials/distributions/02_gig` |
| `gh.md` | Generalized Hyperbolic | `tutorials/core/02_gh_family_tour` |
| `varentropy.md` | Entropy / varentropy / Rényi | `tutorials/stats/03_varentropy` |
